text: Philip William Noel (born June 6, 1931) is an American politician. He was the 68th Governor of Rhode Island. He was elected in 1972, and re-elected in 1974. He was a member of the Democratic Party. ==References== ==Other websites== *Philip William Noel at "The Political Graveyard" Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Rhode Island Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:People from Warwick, Rhode Island
